## Dreamdata Pricing at a Glance

Dreamdata restructured its pricing in 2025, moving from four named tiers (Free/Team/Business/Enterprise) to a product-line model. Here's what each tier costs and includes.

### Free Tier

| Feature | Included |
|---------|----------|
| **Price** | $0/month |
| **Seats** | 5 |
| **History** | 2 months |
| **Attribution models** | 3 (first-touch, last-touch, linear) |
| **Company identification** | Yes (IP-to-company) |
| **Web analytics** | Yes (cookie + cookieless) |
| **Cross-channel cost reporting** | Yes (Google, Meta, LinkedIn, Capterra, G2) |
| **Engagement scoring** | Yes |
| **Ad spend reporting** | Yes |
| **Support** | Self-serve, Slack community, AI chat |

**What's missing from Free:** 360-degree customer journeys, AI Signals, advanced audience building, custom attribution models, BigQuery access.

The free tier is genuinely useful for evaluation — more generous than most competitors. You can identify companies visiting your site, see basic attribution, and track ad spend across channels. The 2-month history limit is the main constraint.

### Activation Starter — From $750/month

| Feature | Included |
|---------|----------|
| **Price** | From $750/month |
| **Billing** | Annual or month-to-month |
| **360-degree customer journeys** | Yes |
| **AI Signals** | Yes (surfaces high-intent accounts) |
| **Advanced audience building** | Yes (sync to LinkedIn, Meta, Google Ads) |
| **Multi-touch attribution models** | Yes (6 models) |
| **Revenue & pipeline analytics** | Yes |
| **Performance analytics / ROAS** | Yes |

This tier adds Dreamdata's standout feature — the 360-degree customer journey visualization that lets you see exactly how accounts progress from first anonymous visit through closed deal. AI Signals automatically surfaces high-intent accounts and notifies your sales team.

The $750/mo starting price represents a ~25% increase from the previous Team plan ($599/mo). Actual cost may be higher depending on data volume and monthly tracked users (MTUs).

### Attribution Advanced — Custom Pricing

| Feature | Included |
|---------|----------|
| **Price** | Contact sales |
| **Custom attribution models** | Yes |
| **AI-powered report summaries** | Yes |
| **Event builder** | Yes |
| **Custom UTM mapping** | Yes |
| **Custom data sources** | Yes |
| **Multiple business units** | Yes |
| **SSO & SAML** | Yes |
| **BigQuery access** | Yes |
| **Dedicated CSM** | Yes |
| **Solutions consulting** | Yes |

This is where Dreamdata's full attribution capabilities live. Custom attribution models, BigQuery data access, and enterprise features like SSO and multi-business-unit support. Pricing requires a sales conversation.

### What Typical Customers Pay

According to Vendr marketplace data, the median Dreamdata annual contract is approximately **$27,000/year** (~$2,250/month). This suggests most paid customers land somewhere between the Activation Starter floor and the Attribution Advanced tier.

