## Dreamdata's 6 Attribution Models

All paid plans include access to these models:

| Model | How It Works |
|-------|-------------|
| **First-touch** | 100% credit to the first interaction |
| **Last-touch** | 100% credit to the final interaction |
| **Linear** | Equal credit across all touchpoints |
| **U-shaped** | 40% first, 40% last, 20% distributed in middle |
| **W-shaped** | 30% first, 30% last, 30% conversion, 10% middle |
| **Data-driven** | Algorithmic — analyzes all journeys dynamically |

Custom attribution models — where you define your own rules — require the Attribution Advanced tier.

