## Bottom Line

Dreamdata's free tier is one of the most generous in B2B attribution — worth trying before evaluating paid tools. The Activation Starter at $750/mo is reasonable for mid-market B2B teams who need journey visualization and LinkedIn audience activation.

The key question: **do you need custom attribution models?** If yes, you're looking at Attribution Advanced (custom pricing, likely $2,000+/mo based on Vendr data). If basic models are sufficient, Activation Starter covers most B2B teams.

If Dreamdata is too expensive, mbuzz ($29-299/mo) and Factors.ai ($399/mo) offer multi-touch attribution at significantly lower price points — though neither matches Dreamdata's journey visualization depth.

